 100%; }</code></pre>\n									<h2>Blockquotes</h2>\n									<p>Let’s keep it simple.</p>\n									<blockquote>\n										<p>Good afternoon, gentlemen. I am a HAL 9000 computer. I became operational at the H.A.L. plant in Urbana, Illinois on the 12th of January 1992. My instructor was Mr. Langley, and he taught me to sing a song. If you’d like to hear it I can sing it for you. <cite>&mdash; <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HAL_9000\">HAL 9000</a></cite></p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:html -->		', 'Sample Page', '\n						', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2019-03-15 05:08:32', '2019-03-15 05:08:32', '', 0, 'https://demo.themefreesia.com/shoppingcart/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
